value.string: Two Story house with 7 bedroom with 3.5 bath. Upgrade flooring and kitchen cabinets with new counter tops. Please don't disturb tenants. Please allow 48 hours to show.

Affordable East end home about 14 miles from town. This cute 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath was just recently painted inside and out. Laminent flooring was installed in living room and new vinyl in bathrooms. Located in a nice quiet neighborhood on the east side of Molokai. Home is close to the elementary school, small neighborhood store and many great east end beaches. Ride bikes along the country road. Currently rented long term so call for showings. Listor is a licensed Broker in Hawaii.
